overview: Gerry Dee: New Year’s Eve Special is a one-hour television comedy special recorded at the Centrepointe Theatre in Ottawa. Hailed as one of Canada’s best comedians, Gerry will be ringing in the New Year with his own unique brand of stand-up.
tagline: Gerry will be ringing in the New Year with his own unique brand of stand-up.
title: Gerry Dee: New Year’s Eve 2013
